Association of dietary flavan-3-ol intakes with plasma phenyl--valerolactones: analysis from the TUDA cohort of healthy older adults.
Of 9 PVL metabolites investigated, two were detected in the majority of samples and were weakly associated with intakes of total F3O and procyanidins+(epi)catechins. Future controlled feeding studies are required to validate plasma PVLs as biomarkers of these dietary polyphenols.
